---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="ホーム">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          <span class="title-line title-line-1">Create Value Beyond Borders</span>
          <span class="title-line title-line-2">国を超え価値を創造する</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          イーエントリー株式会社は、企業のグローバル展開と<br class="desktop-only">
          革新的なビジネスモデルの実現をサポートします
        </p>
       </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">事業内容</h2>
      
      <div class="service-grid">
        <div class="service-card featured">
          <div class="new-badge">NEW</div>
          <div class="service-image-wrapper">
            <img src="/images/services/wellness.jpg" alt="ウェルネス事業" class="service-card-image">
          </div>
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>ウェルネス事業</h3>
          <p>健康寿命の延伸を目指し、がん共済、健康モニタリング、予防医療情報を提供。皆さまの健康な人生を支援します。</p>
          <a href="/wellness.html" class="service-link">詳しく見る →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-image-wrapper">
            <img src="/images/services/global.jpg" alt="グローバル進出コンサルティング" class="service-card-image">
          </div>
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/>
              <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>グローバル進出コンサルティング</h3>
          <p>海外市場への進出を戦略立案から実行までトータルサポート。現地ネットワークと豊富な経験で成功へ導きます。</p>
          <a href="/services.html#global" class="service-link">詳しく見る →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-image-wrapper">
            <img src="/images/services/consulting.jpg" alt="経営／ITコンサルタント派遣" class="service-card-image">
          </div>
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>経営／ITコンサルタント派遣</h3>
          <p>経験豊富なコンサルタントを派遣し、経営課題の解決とITシステムの最適化を実現します。</p>
          <a href="/services.html#consulting" class="service-link">詳しく見る →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-image-wrapper">
            <img src="/images/services/social.jpg" alt="社会的事業支援" class="service-card-image">
          </div>
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 2v6m0 0L9 5m3 3 3-3"/>
              <path d="M12 22v-6m0 0-3 3m3-3 3 3"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/>
              <path d="M4.93 4.93l4.24 4.24m0 0L7 7m2.17 2.17L7 11.34"/>
              <path d="M19.07 19.07l-4.24-4.24m0 0L17 17m-2.17-2.17L17 12.66"/>
              <path d="M19.07 4.93l-4.24 4.24m0 0L17 7m-2.17 2.17L17 11.34"/>
              <path d="M4.93 19.07l4.24-4.24m0 0L7 17m2.17-2.17L7 12.66"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>社会的事業支援</h3>
          <p>ソーシャルビジネスの立ち上げから運営まで、持続可能な社会貢献型ビジネスモデルを支援します。</p>
          <a href="/services.html#social" class="service-link">詳しく見る →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>まずはお気軽にご相談ください</h2>
        <p>貴社のビジネス課題について、専門コンサルタントが無料でご相談を承ります</p>
        <a href="/contact.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">お問い合わせはこちら</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 70px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    margin-top: 70px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background-image: url('/images/hero/hero-bg.png');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center right;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    opacity: 0.7;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(5, 7, 20, 0.85) 0%, rgba(5, 7, 20, 0.4) 50%, rgba(5, 7, 20, 0.1) 100%);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .hero-content {
    text-align: center;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4.8vw, 2.7rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .title-line {
    display: block;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
  }

  .title-line-1 {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff 0%, #0066ff 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5.5vw, 3.2rem);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    animation: slideInUp 1s ease-out 0.3s forwards;
  }

  .title-line-2 {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 4vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    animation: slideInUp 1s ease-out 0.6s forwards;
  }

  @keyframes slideInUp {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.25rem);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.9s forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 1.2s forwards;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff 0%, #0066ff 100%);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .btn-large {
    padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .services {
    padding: 5rem 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .service-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 0;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .service-card.featured {
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }

  .new-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 15px;
    right: 15px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ff4757 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    z-index: 10;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.4);
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .service-image-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    overflow: hidden;
    position: relative;
  }

  .service-card-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service-card:hover .service-card-image {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .service-card > *:not(.service-image-wrapper) {
    padding-left: 2rem;
    padding-right: 2rem;
  }

  .service-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .service-icon svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .service-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .service-link {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: gap 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .service-link:hover {
    transform: translateX(5px);
  }

  .cta {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1) 0%, rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.125rem);
  }

  .mobile-only {
    display: none;
  }

  .desktop-only {
    display: inline;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 70px);
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }

    .hero::before {
      background-position: 70% center;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }

    .hero::after {
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5, 7, 20, 0.7) 0%, rgba(5, 7, 20, 0.5) 50%, rgba(5, 7, 20, 0.7) 100%);
    }

    .services {
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }

    .service-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .cta {
      padding: 3rem 0;
    }

    .cta-content {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .mobile-only {
      display: inline;
    }

    .desktop-only {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>